{"tid":1182817,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《Isle of Dogs / 犬之島》","createTime":"2019-06-02T12:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T12:46:24.000Z","uid":76885,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fa34debd1d7ee23fed05a231d113e94f5f3a4888","tid":1182817,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:46:24.000Z","msg":"1<br />\n好鍾意狗仔擬人咁主導故事發展。<br />\n<br />\nBackground music、聲效，特別係日本有節奏既鼓聲，好深刻。<br />\n一d無對白既畫面，都變得好好睇。<br />\n<br />\n角色講日文，無字幕；英文有字幕；<br />\n好鍾意對日文唔理解種狀態，似以狗仔既角度唔理解人既言語？<br />\n<br />\n種極權，都係大路既極權？<br />\n唔特別有insight。<br />\n<br />\nOverall，我覺得無冷場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n<em>犬之島Isle Of Dogs電影影評 香港人睇特別有Feel</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2018/04/isle-of-dogs-movie-review-hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2018%2F04%2Fisle-of-dogs-movie-review-hk%2F&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI5vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=dfc05213\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2018/04/isle-of-dogs-movie-review-hk/</a><br />\n//<em>講幾句個故事先，話說二十年後日本狗隻太多，市長頒佈緊急法令將所有狗流放到垃圾「犬之島」但後來有人到島上想找回愛犬，開始發覺成個計劃，原來都只係國家陰謀。</em><br />\n<br />\n<em>【有雷影評】《犬之島》狗狗的背後難題</em><br />\n<a href=\"http://loory.tw/2018-06-01-82/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Floory.tw%2F2018-06-01-82%2F&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI5vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=59eaee2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://loory.tw/2018-06-01-82/</a><br />\n<em>《犬之島》是一部美國喜劇動畫電影，由曾以《歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店》聞名的導演魏斯安德森執導，繼《超級狐狸先生》之後，魏斯安德森再度把定格動畫技術發揮至巔峰，承襲他近乎「強迫症」對稱性的畫面美學與構圖巧思，配合獨特冷調幽默感，成功把《犬之島》塑造一個專屬於狗狗的反烏托邦寓言。</em><br />\n<br />\n<em>《犬之島》癲才優異動畫</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/art/%E7%8A%AC%E4%B9%8B%E5%B3%B6-%E7%99%B2%E6%89%8D%E5%84%AA%E7%95%B0%E5%8B%95%E7%95%AB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fart%2F%25E7%258A%25AC%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%25B3%25B6-%25E7%2599%25B2%25E6%2589%258D%25E5%2584%25AA%25E7%2595%25B0%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2595%25AB%2F&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI5vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=eda8a150\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fart%2F%25E7%258A%25AC%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%25B3%25B6-%25E7%2599%25B2%25E6%2589%258D%25E5%2584%25AA%25E7%2595%25B0%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2595%25AB%2F&h=94675c6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/art/%E7%8A%AC%E4%B9%8B%E5%B3%B6-%E7%99%B2%E6%89%8D%E5%84%AA%E7%95%B0%E5%8B%95%E7%95%AB/</a><br />\n<em>韋斯安德遜早已拍過定格動畫，就是 2009 年《狐狸先生無得頂 (Fantastic Mr.Fox) 》 。他的真人怪雞喜劇不少，例如《癲才一族》、《小學雞私奔記》和得獎叫座的《布達佩斯大酒店》，並非片片都好，但都有癲才特色。</em><br />\n<br />\n3<br />\n睇過既人仔，有無咩睇後感？<br />\n<br />\n又有無人有睇過佢其他作品？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}